Genre: Adventure
Developer: League of Geeks 
About the game: Armello is a grim fairy-tale board game come to life. Full of swashbuckling adventure combining deep, tactical card play, rich tabletop strategy and RPG elements. Wage epic single and multiplayer battles, cast spells, hire agents, and prepare poisons and ruses on your quest for the throne!

Minimum Requirements: 
OS: Windows 7 (32-Bit) 
Processor: Dual-core 2.0 GHz 
Memory: 2 GB RAM 
Graphics: DirectX 10 class GPU with 512MB VRAM 
DirectX: Version 9.0c 
Hard Drive: 4 GB available space

How to install: 
1. Mount with Daemon Tools or burn iso.
2. Install the game!
3. Copy crack from &quot;CODEX&quot; folder and paste in game directory!
4. Play and Enjoy!

